metadata.description:
Before I Die was a song I made in a time where I felt scared to show myself in the world but deep down I also knew that theres so much I want to do and experience in this world. This record is about recognizing ones own potential, risking everything to go after your vision and not listening to anybody outside of yourself.
Alot of my music reflects my life growing up, wanting to be understood and exposing my vulnerabilities in hopes it will help others to open up about whatever they are going through.
